20
00:01:56,046 --> 00:01:59,641
Sometimes I don't even know
who you are anymore.

21
00:02:01,185 --> 00:02:04,279
Ha! Look like Milhouse's mom
finally threw out his blankie.

22
00:02:04,388 --> 00:02:06,356
He'll pay a lot to get this back.

23
00:02:06,457 --> 00:02:09,017
Especially when we send it
to him piece by piece.

24
00:02:09,126 --> 00:02:11,390
<i>- [ Both Laughing ]
- [ Groaning ]</i>

25
